title: Formation Mission: Balanced Squad

title: Formation Mission: Long Ranged Squad
content: Form an Echelon with 2 HGs, 2 RFs, and 1 SMG. (P.S. This setup has excellent damage and can quickly dispatch the enemy back line.)

title: Formation Mission: Burst Damage Squad
content: Form an Echelon with 2 SMGs, 2 MGs, and 1 HG. (P.S. This setup can deal huge amounts of damage up front but will have noticible amounts of downtime for reloading.)

title: Formation Mission: Support Squad
content: Form an Echelon with 5 HGs. (P.S. This setup consumes very little resources. It is very useful as a backup Echelon and can be used for capturing nodes.)

title: Formation Mission: Elite Squad
content: Form an Echelon with 2 SGs, 2 MGs, and 1 HG. (P.S. SGs have strong defensive capabilities and provide buffs to MGs. They are only available from T-Doll Heavy Production.)

title: Tactical Doll: Beginner Exam
content: You will need to capture Heliport by encirclement to obtain sufficient action points in order to pass the exam.

title: Tactical Doll: Elementary Exam
content: You will need to observe your enemies and familiarize yourself with the features of different gun types in order to pass the exam.

title: Tactical Doll: Intermediate Exam
content: You will need a strong understanding of the features of different gun types in order to pass the exam.

title: Tactical Doll: Advanced Exam
content: This exam is a comprehensive test of a Commander's abilities.

title: Tactical Doll: Final Exam
content: On top of deploying well-trained T-Dolls, you will also need to demonstrate a good understanding of map mechanisms, gun type advantages, and enemy information in order to pass the exam.

title: Tactical Doll: Gun Types
content: Complete the tutorial and familiarize yourself with what combat situations each gun type is suited for.

title: T-Doll Tutorial: More on Gun Types
content: Complete the tutorial and further understand what combat situations each gun type is suited for.

title: Night Battle: Beginner Exam
content: You will need to understand the importance of Radars and Night Battle Equipment in order to pass the exam.

title: Night Battle: Intermediate Exam
content: You will need to select suitable Equipment when fighting against different types of enemy units in order to pass the exam.

title: Night Battle: Final Exam
content: On top of equipping your T-Dolls with high-quality Equipment, you will also need to demonstrate a good understanding of Night Battle mechanisms and Equipment features in order to pass the exam.

title: Night Battle: Night Battle Equipment
content: Complete the tutorial and learn the functions of Equipment in combat.

title: Night Battle: Night Battle Vision
content: Complete the tutorial and learn how field of vision works in Night Battles.

title: Fairy: Beginner Exam
content: You will need to make good use of Combat Fairies to enhance your echelons' combat capability in order to pass the exam.

title: Fairy: Intermediate Exam
content: You will need to use Strategy Fairies to turn the battle situation to your advantage in order to pass the exam.

title: Fairy: Final Exam
content: On top of high-level Fairies, you will also need to use the Fairies' skills to your advantage in order to pass the final exam.

title: Fairy: Combat Fairy Demonstration

title: Fairy: Strategy Fairy Demonstration

title: Heavy Ordnance Corps: Beginner Exam

title: Heavy Ordnance Corps: Intermediate Exam
content: You will need to use your HOC units to defeat enemies armed with force fields in order to pass the exam.

title: Heavy Ordnance Corps: Final Exam
content: You will need to defeat powerful enemies with high-level HOC units in order to pass the final exam.

title: Coalition Forces: Intermediate Exam
content: You may only clear this stage with Coalition Forces in order to pass the exam.

title: Coalition Forces: Final Exam
content: You will need high-level Coalition Units in order to pass the final exam.
